reviewText: Very interesting course that taught me a lot about music and metaphor in business .
Quiero Agradecer a Coursera por  esta opiortunidad de aprender a traves de esta plataforma, Muchas Gracias

​A source of personal growth. After compleeting this cours I know more about music, metaphor and leadership. Interesting, rewarding, and valuable. I now have gained knowledge that can increase my performance at work. Thank you Dr Amal El-Sawad, and thanks to all my fellow students sharing their knowledge and helping others to grow.
